item.description:
The fact that @cursor_ai  had to post-train its own model and now partner with xAI for compute I assume shows how hard it is to succeed in the ultra competitive AI coding (or just general knowledge work) space without owning full stack.

---
@petergyang | ❤️ 19 | 🔁 1 | 💬 3 | 👁 1078

Multi-model workflows are the real frontier pattern in 2026 — pick the right model for the right job, not one model for everything.
@apolmig using M2.7 for &quot;cost-efficient iteration&quot; on 6.4M views of synthetic data is exactly the shape of workload we built it for. Beautiful work. 
And thanks @ti_guo_ for discover the project!

